This is a configuration setup for awesome. There is everything I need for my desktop environment.

Requirements
============

- Remember to make a symbolic link between system folder to our folder::
    sudo ln -s ~/.config/awesome/themes /usr/share/awesome/themes

- install Vicious: http://awesome.naquadah.org/wiki/Vicious
- install dmenu
- install naughty
- install weather-util
- install g++
- install powersave (manually)
- install build-essential
- install libdbus-glib-1-dev
